"So kho ahaṃ, aggivessana, mukhato ca nāsato ca kaṇṇato ca assāsapassāse "
"uparundhiṃ."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: muddhani → muddhāni (bj) | muddhānaṃ (s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: ūhananti → ūhanti (si) | ohananti (s1-3, km) | uhananti (mr)
msgctxt "mn36:22.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, aggivessana, mukhato ca nāsato ca kaṇṇato ca assāsapassāsesu "
"uparuddhesu adhimattā vātā muddhani ūhananti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: muddhani abhimattheyya → muddhānaṃ abhimantheyya (si, pts1); muddhānaṃ abhimattheyya (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn36:22.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, aggivessana, balavā puriso tiṇhena sikharena muddhani "
"abhimattheyya;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn36:22.6"
msgid ""
"evameva kho me, aggivessana, mukhato ca nāsato ca kaṇṇato ca assāsapassāsesu "
"uparuddhesu adhimattā vātā muddhani ūhananti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn36:22.7"
msgid ""
"Āraddhaṃ kho pana me, aggivessana, vīriyaṃ hoti asallīnaṃ upaṭṭhitā sati "
"asammuṭṭhā. Sāraddho ca pana me kāyo hoti appaṭippassaddho teneva "
"dukkhappadhānena padhānābhitunnassa sato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn36:22.8"
msgid ""
"Evarūpāpi kho me, aggivessana, uppannā dukkhā vedanā cittaṃ na pariyādāya "
"tiṭṭhati."
msgstr ""

